you committed the crime.

233
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:40,081
This will be the last interrogation.

234
00:11:41,321 --> 00:11:42,521
As usual,

235
00:11:43,001 --> 00:11:44,280
confess, plead guilty,

236
00:11:44,641 --> 00:11:46,761
