245
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:08,321
I can give them all

246
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,641
to you.

247
00:12:11,241 --> 00:12:12,521
Let's see

248
00:12:13,121 --> 00:12:14,321
if you

249
00:12:15,441 --> 00:12:16,561
